Analyzing impacts on the alternative splice analysis with MAJIQ

  • read length (U2AF2 & UPF1 gene knockdown)

  • read depth (U2AF2 gene knockdown)

  • sample size (endodermal cell vs H1 cell line)





1 Fasterq-dump - loading FASTQ files from SRA database

fastq-dump --gzip --skip-technical --readids --split-3 --outdir /share/project/zarnack/annika/01_fastq_files/U2AF2/ SRR3469464

# newer and faster --> fasterq-dump
# --skip-technical reads and --split-3 options are default


2 Trimmomatic - read preprocessing \(\bullet\) simulate different read length

1. trim adapters

2. sliding window trimming

3. remove reads shorter than 100 nt

4. trim reads to (100,) 75, 50 and 36 nt

export PATH=~/miniconda3/bin:$PATH

cd /share/project/zarnack/annika/01_fastq_files/U2AF2
read_length=(100 75 50 36)

for length in ${read_length[@]}; do
  for SRR in `ls -1 *_1.fastq.gz | sed 's/\_1.fastq.gz//'`; do                # go through all read pairs
    echo trimmomatic PE $SRR\_1.fastq.gz $SRR\_2.fastq.gz \                   # pass paired forward and reverse reads
    $length\_$SRR\_R1_paired.fastq.gz $length\_$SRR\_R1_unpaired.fastq.gz \   # define 4 output files
    $length\_$SRR\_R2_paired.fastq.gz $length\_$SRR\_R2_unpaired.fastq.gz \   
    ILLUMINACLIP:TruSeq3-PE.fa:2:30:10:8:true \                               # cut adapters                                                        
    SLIDINGWINDOW:4:20 \                                                      # sliding window trimming                                                     
    MINLEN:100 \                                                              # remove reads < 100 nt                            
    CROP:$length >> /share/project/zarnack/annika/02_processed_reads/endodermal_cell/cmd_file_$length     
  done
  bash /share/project/zarnack/annika/02_processed_reads/endodermal_cell/cmd_file_$length                  
done


3 FastQC - quality report

# check if adapters are removed
fastqc *.bam --o /share/project/zarnack/annika/03_star_mapping/U2AF2/


4 STAR - read mapping

read_length=(100 75 50 36)
gtf=/share/project/zarnack/annika/gencode.v41.annotation.gtf
genome=/share/project/zarnack/annika/GRCh38.p13.genome.fa
gd=/share/project/zarnack/annika/genome_indices

# GENERATING GENOME INDEXES for all read length
for length in ${read_length[@]}; do
  STAR \
    --runThreadN 6 \
    --runMode genomeGenerate \     # generate genome files
    --genomeDir $gd/$length \      # path to previously created directory with genome index files 
    --genomeFastaFiles $genome \   # FASTA files with genome reference sequences
    --sjdbGTFfile $gtf \           # path to file with annotated transcripts
    --sjdbOverhang $length-1       # specify max possible overhang for the reads
done 

# READ MAPPING
for length in ${read_length[@]}; do
  for SRR in `ls -1 $length\_*_R1_paired.fastq.gz | sed 's/\_R1_paired.fastq.gz//'`; do  
    STAR \
      --runThreadN 6 \
      --genomeDir $gd/$length \
      --readFilesCommand zcat \                                                         # unzip gzipped files
      --readFilesIn $SRR\_R1_paired.fastq.gz $SRR\_R2_paired.fastq.gz \                 # path to forward and reverse read 
      --outFileNamePrefix /share/project/zarnack/annika/03_star_mapping/U2AF2/$SRR\_ \  # change file prefixes
      --outFilterMultimapNmax 1 \                                                       # max number of multiple alignments allowed for a read
      --outFilterMismatchNmax 999 \                                                     # max number of mismatches per pair --> switched off
      --outFilterMismatchNoverLmax 0.04 \                                               # max number of mismatches per pair relative to read length
      --outSAMtype BAM SortedByCoordinate                                               # set output type to BAM sorted by coordinate
    done
done

6 MAJIQ

6.1 Builder - LSV detection \(\bullet\) simulate different sample size

Configuration file

[info]
readlen=100
bamdirs=/share/project/zarnack/annika/03_star_mapping/U2AF2/read_length/read_length
genome=GRCh38
strandness=reverse

[experiments]
U2AF2_100_KD=U2AF2_100_KD_1,U2AF2_100_KD_2
U2AF2_100_CT=U2AF2_100_CT_1,U2AF2_100_CT_2


LSV detection for different read length

source /home/mario/applications/MAJIQv2.3/bin/activate

# FILES AND DIRS
GFF3="/share/project/zarnack/annika/gencode.v41.annotation.gff3"
CONFIGFILE="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/build"
OUTDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/build"

genes=(U2AF2 UPF1)
read_length=(100 75 50 36)

for gene in ${genes[@]}; do
  for length in ${read_length[@]}; do
    majiq build $GFF3 \
    -c $CONFIGFILE/$gene/read_length/$length/${gene}_${length}_config_file_.txt \
    -j 6 \
    -o $OUTDIR/$gene/read_length/$length
  done
done


LSV detection for different read depth

source /home/mario/applications/MAJIQv2.3/bin/activate

# FILES AND DIRS

for reads in ${reads[@]}; do
  majiq build $GFF3 \

LSV detection for different sample size

source /home/mario/applications/MAJIQv2.3/bin/activate

# FILES AND DIRS
GFF3="/share/project/zarnack/annika/gencode.v41.annotation.gff3"
BUILD="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/build/endodermal_vs_H1/100"

# SAMPLE COMBINATIONS
combos_2er=('_1_2' '_1_3' '_2_3')

# MAJIQ BUILD 
# 2 samples
for combi in ${combos_2er[@]}; do
  majiq build $GFF3 \
  -c $BUILD/2_samples/sample$combi/endo_vs_H1_100_config_file_2_samples$combi.txt \
  -j 6 \
  -o $BUILD/2_samples/sample$combi
done

# 3 samples
majiq build $GFF3 \
-c $BUILD/3_samples/endo_vs_H1_100_config_file_3_samples.txt \
-j 6 \
-o $BUILD/3_samples


6.2 Quantifier - LSV quantification \(\Delta\Psi\)

source /home/mario/applications/MAJIQv2.3/bin/activate

# FILES AND DIRS
BUILDDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/build"
OUTDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/dpsi"

genes=(U2AF2 UPF1)
read_length=(100 75 50 36)

for gene in ${genes[@]}; do
  for length in ${read_length[@]}; do
  majiq deltapsi \
  -grp1 \
  "${BUILDDIR}/$gene/read_length/$length/${gene}_${length}_KD_1.majiq" \
  "${BUILDDIR}/$gene/read_length/$length/${gene}_${length}_KD_2.majiq" \
  -grp2 \
  "${BUILDDIR}/$gene/read_length/$length/${gene}_${length}_CT_1.majiq" \
  "${BUILDDIR}/$gene/read_length/$length/${gene}_${length}_CT_2.majiq" \
  --names $gene\_$length\_KD $gene\_$length\_CT \
  -j 6 \
  --output-type voila \
  -o $OUTDIR/$gene/read_length/$length/
  done
done


7 Voila - visualize LSVs

7.1 Voila TSV - generate TSV files

source /home/mario/applications/MAJIQv2.3/bin/activate

# FILES AND DIRS
BUILDDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/build/"
DPSIDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/dpsi/"
OUTDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/voila/"

genes=(U2AF2 UPF1)
readLength=(100 75 50 36)

# MAJIQ Voila
# U2AF2 and UPF1
for GENE in ${genes[@]}; do
  for LENGTH in ${readLength[@]}; do
    voila tsv \
    -f "${OUTDIR}/${GENE}/thresholds_0.05/${LENGTH}/${GENE}_${LENGTH}_KD_vs_CT_voila.tsv" \
    --show-all \
    --threshold 0.05 \
    --changing-between-group-dpsi 0.05 \
    --non-changing-between-group-dpsi 0.05 \
    -j 6 \
    "${BUILDDIR}/${GENE}/${LENGTH}/splicegraph.sql" \
    "${DPSIDIR}/${GENE}/${LENGTH}/${GENE}_${LENGTH}_KD-${GENE}_${LENGTH}_CT.deltapsi.voila"   
  done   
done


7.2 Voila Modulize - LSV classification

source /home/mario/applications/MAJIQv2.3/bin/activate

#FILES AND DIRS
BUILDDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/build/U2AF2/read_depth"
DPSIDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/04_majiq/dpsi/U2AF2/read_depth"
OUTDIR="/share/project/zarnack/annika/06_modulize/U2AF2/read_depth"

read_depth=(30M 25M 20M 15M 10M 5M 2_5M 1M)

# voila modulize U2AF2
for reads in ${read_depth[@]}; do
  voila modulize \
  --changing-between-group-dpsi 0.05 \
  --non-changing-between-group-dpsi 0.05 \
  --changing-between-group-dpsi-secondary 0.025 \
  --show-all \
  -j 6 \
  -d "${OUTDIR}/${reads}" \
  "${BUILDDIR}/${reads}/splicegraph.sql" \
  "${DPSIDIR}/${reads}/U2AF2_KD_${reads}_reads-U2AF2_CT_${reads}_reads.deltapsi.voila"
done
